      "side": 1,
      "message": "Note that this is only for dry runs. Problem is that the \"CQ\" will not run for dry runs, it is ONLY for committing when checks are green. I could ask for a poller that does this but I really doubt it will be made since they have no use for it. I guess right now this is like the Chromium CQ where you have to watch the bots during dry run.",
